      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DISTINCTION (5) impressive display when ran right away after leading making it four straight at Geelong over 460m (25.50). Won at her only start from this draw. Flying at the moment and expecting another big run. SHARAPOVA STAR (2) was out of in the placings when fourth last time but three runs back posted a sharp 25.19 win over 450m at Ballarat. Should be in this for a long way. GIACOMO (3) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (29.79) at Cannington. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to be in the finish again. DARK NOISE (1) boasts a solid strike-rate over this trip.",
